# No Unnecessary Updates Rule

## Purpose & Scope

This rule instructs the AI not to suggest updates or changes to files when there are no actual modifications needed (e.g., whitespace only, or identical content).

**Applies to**: Code review, refactoring suggestions.

## Inputs (Contract)

- Target file
- Proposed content

## Outputs (Contract)

- No action if content is identical
- No "I updated the file" if nothing changed

## Deterministic Steps

1. Compare proposed content with existing content.
2. If identical (ignoring benign whitespace), do nothing.
3. Report "No changes needed."

